subject_information.comments: The instructions were kind of confusing and I failed one of the questions the first time.  There is actually no mention in the instructions that says the listener can use the chat.
subject_information.strategy: I tried to keep what I said simple.  If I could see all the objects and all I needed was to describe the color and shape, that's all I said.  If I couldn't see every object I would describe the color, shape, and the inside pattern.
